---
// DisclosureBanner — strbuyers-novel. Top-of-page regulatory chrome that
// links to /disclosures (page itself comes Phase 3 Task 22). Small, clear,
// non-disruptive. Visible on every page that hosts an AffiliateBlock.
---
<aside
  class="disclosure-banner border-b border-rule bg-parchment-alt print:hidden"
  aria-label="Affiliate disclosure"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-2 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2">
    <p class="text-caption text-ink-2 leading-snug">
      Some links on this site are paid partnerships. We never recommend a vendor we wouldn't use ourselves.
    </p>
    <a
      href="/disclosures"
      class="text-caption text-[color:var(--accent-700)] underline-offset-2 hover:underline whitespace-nowrap"
    >
      Read the disclosures →
    </a>
  </div>
</aside>
